videos.description: Pittsburgh's Michael Young receives a pass on the baseline then finishes with a two hand slam.
videos.headline: Young slams one on Syracuse defender

videos.description: Pittsburgh's Jamel Artis tosses backwards to an open Cameron Johnson who catches and connects on a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Johnson puts in a 3-pointer in transition

videos.description: Syracuse's John Gillon cuts through the lane then finishes the bucket plus the foul.
videos.headline: Gillon finishes tough lay-in

videos.description: Pittsburgh's Michael Young spins, draws a foul, and scores to extend the Panther's lead.
videos.headline: Young makes athletic play to score and draw a foul

videos.description: Pittsburgh's Jamel Artis tosses a nice pass inside to Michael Young who goes up and finishes with a dunk.
videos.headline: Artis bounce pass sets up Young catch and slam

videos.description: Pittsburgh moves the ball around and finds Cameron Johnson in the corner who connects on a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Johnson sends in a 3-pointer
